title: Back to the 80's Cigars
itunes:title: Back to the 80's Cigars
description: We're smoking cigars from the 1980's! House of Winsor Panatella Claro humidified from the 1980 Olympics, and Macanudo Vintage 1988 humidified for over 25 years. Special guest Duane Morency, Two Guys Smoke Shop Manager and cigar specialist joins The Cigar Authority to give us the real "dirt" on Dave.
